common_text_3486:
1. During the Kingdom Group Purchase, a group purchase promotion will be carried out every 24 hours. Group Purchase Pack prices will be settled after one round and the corresponding packs will be sent by mail; 
2.Group Purchase Packs cant be purchased during settlement; 
3.Players can purchase at most 10 Group Purchase Packs during each round of promotion; 
4.The more packs sold during the Kingdom Group Purchase, the better the rewards included in each Group Purchase Pack.

common_text_3570:
1.There are four leagues of different ranks, listed here from lowest to highest: Novice League->Rookie League->Elite League->Master League. 
2. Alliances participating for the first time will start in the Novice League. 
3. Alliances which ranked in the Top 5 and reached Mission Phase 8+ in each league rank are able to earn ranking rewards and be promoted to the next league for the next round of the event. 
4. Alliances which ranked in the Bottom 5 will be demoted a league rank for the next round. 
5. Mission attempts and claimable phase rewards will change among different league ranks: In the Master League, each alliance member can accept 9 missions and claim 24 phase rewards; 
In the Elite League, each alliance member can accept 8 missions and claim 21 phase rewards; 
In the Rookie League, each alliance member can accept 7 missions and claim 18 phase rewards; 
And in the Novice League, each alliance member can accept 6 missions and claim 15 phase rewards.

common_text_3718:
1. The event lasts for eight days. For the first five days a different themed event will be unlocked each day. These can be completed during the first seven days of the event. On the eighth day players can claim chests as a reward:
2. On the eighth day of the event players claim chests based on the number of task rewards they have claimed. Claimed chests can then be found in players bags;
3. When the event finishes, prizes and progress will be deleted, so make sure you claim everything from the event interface before the time runs out.

